Name:           glib
Version:        0.11.1
License:        LGPL-2.1
License-file:   COPYING
Copyright:      (c) 2001-2010 The Gtk2Hs Team
Author:         Axel Simon, Duncan Coutts
Maintainer:     gtk2hs-users@sourceforge.net
